<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<appendix xml:id="app-binomial-table">
  <title>Binomial Distribution</title>

  <p>This appendix gives a compact <term>binomial table<idx><h>appendices</h><h>binomial table</h></idx></term> of exact probabilities <m>P(X=k)</m> for <m>X\sim B(n,p)</m>, with <m>n</m> from 1 to 10 and several common values of <m>p</m>. If <m>p&gt;0.5</m>, use the symmetry relation <m>P_p(X=k)=P_{1-p}(X=n-k)</m>.</p>
  <p>Each table lists probabilities rounded to four decimal places. To make the print version easier to read, each value of <m>p</m> is split into a lower-<m>k</m> table and an upper-<m>k</m> table. For larger values of <m>n</m> or for parameters not shown here, use technology.</p>

